Doremy Vernon https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Doremy_Vernon 0 Doremy Vernon is an English actress and former Tiller Girl who was born in London, England, and is best known for playing Diana Yardswick, the canteen manageress in the long-running BBC comedy Are You Being Served?.
